<h2> Publications : </h2>
Well, since I am a doctorate candidate, I guess I have to show that I have published something. 
<ul>
<li> Angelopoulou, Elli,   Tsai-Hong, Hong,  and Wu, Angela. <!WA18><a href = "http://www.cs.jhu.edu/~angelop/world.dvi">"World Model Representation."</a> Proceedings IEEE Intelligent Vehicles 92. 
