<li> Wolff, Lawrence B. and Angelopoulou, Elli. <!WA19><a href = "http://www.cs.jhu.edu/~angelop/3D_stereo.ECCV94.ps"> "3-D Stereo Using Photometric Ratios." </a> Proceedings of 3rd European Conference in Computer Vision (ECCV) 1994, Lecture Notes in Computer Science, Vol. 801, pp. 247-258.
